lenders.name: Myrna
lenders.loan_because: I need funds for fertilizer and other expenses that come with farming like irrigation, other worker's labor, and fuel for tractors, irrigation machine, etc.
lenders.occupational_info: I own a farm, but because of typhoons that always hit our country, it's very hard to maintain it. I plant rice, corn, and other vegetables and sell it to buyers, and markets. Rice and corn field are very hard to maintain especially during rainy season, that's why I spend a lot of money before I could even sell it. So, I'm hoping for your kind hearts to help me fund my farm and expand it and get more profit from it.
